Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚  优子  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  傻站在这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看  这个粘在我的额头上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚发现？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一如既往的天然呆呢  伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小～伦伦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的电视剧有看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了看了  很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:17.93,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦的男性朋友很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就精神焕发的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  透
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,180)}喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也还是那么小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱摸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会弄得这么脏啊  跌倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是被伦给欺负了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她追着蝴蝶差点儿被车撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真伟大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么中午见  透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那啥  现在去你家可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  那么一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为考试  所以有一阵子没见到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小透  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久疏问候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦在楼上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦会高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  我考上了和小伦一样的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  透
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什…什…什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  这小鬼是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  这个人是谁  刚刚那是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你合格了呀  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格什么的无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子就是透？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好小呢  你想介绍给我们的就是这个孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介绍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是发表合格的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你可能会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喊她们俩过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在学校的朋友  优子和渚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天你们就可以多多交流啦  透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉被她死死的盯着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给人的第一印象太差了  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事快给人好好解释下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  你误会了  刚才是伦她在挠我痒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可没有做什么奇怪的事  只是在玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你偷袭我干嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就可以打成一片真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去阻止她们真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我发选修的讲义了  去年也做过的  你们懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的班主任还真是个够随意的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  抄在黑板上的就是需要提交的选修课选单的写法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么人有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选修课对于一年级来说还不多  学年越高选修课就会越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也和你们的未来息息相关  请认真的考虑后再做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要特别谈话的人  随时都可以来找老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦她没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在搞什么飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  吃饭饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真性急啊  透她还没过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢  一时没注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来了哟  渚  真不愧是透呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…她听到刚才的召唤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个松鼠牙签好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  是我很中意的一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢动物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那伦喜欢的动物是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是鸟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹦鹉什么的吗  真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦的脑袋真像鹦鹉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说都很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？你说的是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃鹦鹉也太残忍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是吐槽点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦她只是喜欢吃鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你喜欢吃的食物是鸡肉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不过只要是肉的话我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次我们一起去吃烤肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃牛背肉和盐烤牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子好想吃烤肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能够听到烤肉的声音在内心深处的某个地方回响了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信提示音！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦的鸡蛋烧好像很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我吃一口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伦做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两位的关系真的不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真叫做「关系不错」吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当真的很好吃呢  透～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…伦  你要往哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的教室是这边才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  因为前一阵子还是一年级生  不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透也是  再不快点回教室的话就赶不上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  透～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  下午的课你没有睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  下午完全没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才差点从窗户掉下去让你清醒了不少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  要注意点才行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下午倒是比较犯困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  为了消除困意来吃点糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  也给伦一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一颗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就给透留着了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话伦你那份就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我和她一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦可真温柔呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗糖…要怎样才能对半分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刀～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能切成两半了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来  为了一块糖球而受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像笨蛋一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到地上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可嘱咐过你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为没关系的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有糖的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  还有糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖  糖  糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记扔包装袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透真厉害啊  连空袋子的味道都闻得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透最喜欢甜食了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  刚才大家吃掉的已经是最后一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会带些来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃麦芽糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  还是吃点不甜的或者能控制卡路里的点心比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  甜的比较好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  知道了  明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩选修课是怎么决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镰手先生说过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦那时候在打瞌睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那时候优子为什么摔倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时伦好像要倒下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要接住她  然而伦突然停了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就失去平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  透的一年级选修课选了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和小伦在一起…上一样的课
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小伦在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不会改变的哦…我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  透  以后大家一起来喝茶聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了  优子  让我也抱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  透
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  伦的男性朋友真的很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聊些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我优子的三围吧  小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保密哦  从上到下是88·56·87
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！  厉害爆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这之类的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你知道我的尺寸啊  渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见哦  小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什么啊  这就不聊了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  透～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都是如此有干劲呢  透
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  按照约定我带了糖来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿和大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:16.74,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不要～  呜呜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两位的关系真的不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到雨的种类  那可真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是毛毛雨  小雨  还有泪雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想不到你知道的可真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来问个问题吧  美宝莲  
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:05.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷对美穂（ミホ）的爱称（ミポリン）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么题？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着…刚才你是不是已经把我的名字说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  柚多谷我真是大失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  A频道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.90,0:24:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天就来泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  话都说到这地步了  莫非下周我们就要登场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------INJP-----------------
